data.description: Welcome to the gated community of Davis Estates, centrally located within the city limits of Saint Cloud Florida!  From the moment you walk up to the paver front entry you will notice the meticulous care of this 5 year new home.  This open concept home is perfect for entertaining as the heart of this home is the kitchen that over looks the living room and enclosed back patio.  With Stainless appliances, wood cabinets and granite counter tops, this spacious kitchen is sure to make even the pickiest of chef's happy. This 2400 sq ft home showcases 4 bedrooms with one being a 2nd Master Suite, and an Office/Den that can easily become a 5th bedroom.  Don't stress about a high electric bill as this newer home offers all Energy Efficient/Hurricane windows and extra insulation in the attic.  This move in ready home is waiting for a new owner to make a lifetime of memories, schedule your showing today!
